Een getrouwd stel (Ryan Kwanten en Amy Smart) zit samen met hun twee oude vrienden

English
On May 12th, Vista Pacific Flight 7500 departs Los Angeles International Airport
bound for Tokyo. The take-off is routine but what transpires over the next ten hours
is anything but ordinary. As the overnight flight makes its way over the
Pacific Ocean, the passengers encounter what appears to be a supernatural force in
the cabin.
